snippet.title: PM Modi Asks Opposition To Join 'Crusade' Against Black Money

localized.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi today sought the opposition's cooperation on demonetisation, asserting that the government has launched a "crusade" against corruption and black money with the decision to ban 500 and 1000 rupee notes.
